                <h2 class="sec-h" style="font-size:2rem;text-align:left">A Legacy of <span>Technical Education</span></h2>
                <p class="story-p">Shri Bhairavnath Nisarg Mandals Polytechnic was established with a vision to bring quality diploma-level engineering education to the Aurangabad region. Located at <strong>Gevrai Tanda, Paithan Road, Aurangabad</strong>, the college is affiliated to <strong>MSBTE</strong> and approved by <strong>DTE Maharashtra</strong>.</p>
                <p class="story-p">We offer diploma programmes in Computer Science, Mechanical, Civil, Electrical Engineering, and uniquely in <strong>Food Technology</strong> — one of the few polytechnics in the region with this specialization.</p>
